data.description: Take a look at this spacious 3-bedroom 2 bath log home with a great floor plan. Tall pine cathedral ceilings and walls, skylights. Country kitchen is a cook's delight, plenty of cabinets and workspace. Dining room, large living room, brick hearth and cozy, warm   woodburning stove. Also, two bedrooms and bath on the main floor. Upstairs you have the primary bedroom suite. Walkout basement boasts of a family room, bar with dining too. Bonus room, laundry and utility room. Back screened porch sits high for the views. Walk out to the covered, screened hammock for relaxing., sitting area and workshop. Rural setting. But close to Freeport/Bath/ Topsham Brunswick Augusta and L/A. This is the home you have been searching for.
